Package DAO

package DAO
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AppointmentDao
    This class is responsible for the jdbc queries to the appointments table in the database.
    ContactsDao
    This class is responsible for doing jdbc queries to the Contacts table in the database.
    CustomersDao
    This class is responsible for doing jdbc queries to the customer table, the first level division table, and the countries table.
    DatabaseConnection
    This class is used to create a connection to the database, and to close the connection when done.
    ReportsDao
    This class is responsible for doing the database queries for the reports and holding the reports observable lists.
    UserDao
    This class is responsible for the jdbc queries to the users table.
